{"tid":158944,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求伊貝扭蛋","createTime":"2017-03-16T15:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T02:44:30.000Z","uid":1260,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc689265125844215ee6eff53e11d7b7afea55d","tid":158944,"uid":1260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"早排見有得扭，前前後後扭左七隻<br />\n點知搵左幾區啲機都冇貨<br />\n一上網搵原來成四年前既野黎<br />\n依家差冰 雷 月，唔想買多成set<br />\n有冇人之前扭落可以讓埋俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6F6d6y6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6F6d6y6.jpg&h=7a945ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43B7A6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43B7A6W.jpg&h=f3cea67f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c58e3364a7daa0acf0aeccff965d34bce0833a75","tid":158944,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"呢套出左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmegabox都好似仲有"},{"pid":"d880ac7e2b0d982d10156be440191daf35229b77","tid":158944,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套出左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmegabox都好似仲有</blockquote><br />\n呢套野我第一次扭已經係3年前"},{"pid":"436d3e297ee2a2ae593d47934750f7d13038572f","tid":158944,"uid":1260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢套出左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmegabox都好似仲有</blockquote><br />\n呢套野我第一次扭已經係3年前</blockquote><br />\nMEGABOX搵過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係早半個月係九龍灣見到..扭左幾隻...<br />\n之後荃灣同觀塘都有以為出左冇耐<br />\n原來係13年出既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5cffbd1f6f56dd6d24f1ef2078e71a43fe3125","tid